{"tid":1466492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"豬隊友唔該入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:48.000Z","uid":8486,"like":71,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4acd319b319af3c5210a90533ff26a58db30e4ee","tid":1466492,"uid":8486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地對唔對得住女義士隻眼呀?</span></span><br />\n唔該你地返去諗清楚<br />\n黑警話撚咗你聽有鬼啦<br />\n咁都比人煽動到<br />\n<br />\n如果你地覺得自己喺容易比人煽動嘅<br />\n麻煩你返屋企做冷氣軍師<br />\n唔好再出嚟害d手足<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆嘅前提喺<br />\n大家都用唔同方法幫緊件事<br />\n<br />\n唔喺好似你地咁鬧救護鬧記者<br />\n仲要歡呼 以為圍住公安幾個鐘就覺得自己贏咗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求你地贏咗邊樣?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我理撚得你話我喺鬼<br />\n我對你地真喺好撚失望"},{"pid":"5159a02978e50d87f4e9bed562ffbe32349983fa","tid":1466492,"uid":95487,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca49d15f1a988cfaeb795414dd7f12605a7d196","tid":1466492,"uid":8486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔諗清楚 唔該你地唔好出嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b55d81af52473b62dd1812a6b8c3e576ea92d54","tid":1466492,"uid":8486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔諗清楚 唔該你地唔好出嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"39f7aaefe5162136feac139906db21f05e9a9af8","tid":1466492,"uid":8486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔諗清楚 唔該你地唔好出嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"76dcc655f99e7502b6cddc4e9b8cf11aa34bb281","tid":1466492,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d940f15b0576deab03802683b50f99d0ecfac68","tid":1466492,"uid":283021,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"條友仲開記招！ 非法禁固呀家陣, 搵人提佢收皮啦 危險呀"},{"pid":"ff7e0dc5d8c19d79af5b10b37967cc384628f6e6","tid":1466492,"uid":8486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔諗清楚 唔該你地唔好出嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"955961f2403de56622cab6cf1d54a5a481f3fb3b","tid":1466492,"uid":8486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔諗清